4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become cybersecurity specialists without prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks, featuring three live online classes weekly with a maximum of 16 participants. Students gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside advanced training in cloud security, penetration testing, and risk management. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by multiple institutions. Classes are available in English and Spanish, tailored to the chosen campus language. For further details, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop